steps.name: Maker is redirected to Customer Apporval Page and View all the details wrt to customer
The maker will accept the request if all requirements are met accordingly.
Maker select the Industry ISIC Code of Customer and click on Approve
Clicking on notfication the Maker Status has changed from Pending to Approved
Maker Logout clicking on Profile
Checker Login with the Username and Password and click on Sign me in
Checker will be landed on dashboard and clicks on notification
Select the Pending Approval Request
Checker is redirected to customer Approval and click on Accept Request
Checker Select Industry ISIC Code and click on approve or deny.
Alert Popup is displayed and click on OK.
Checker is redirected to customer approval table and now the final status is changed to Approved for the concer customer
Checker clicks on Profile and Logout.
